name: Easter Funny Bunny Screen Printed Plush
description:
He’s the geekiest Easter Bunny you’ll ever see.  He’s hand screen printed from an original design by me in white ink on brown felt.  I use water based non toxic inks.
Funny Bunny measures 8” tall and comes wrapped like a real chocolate bunny, but with zero calories!

name: The Pirate Cupcake Adult T Shirt
description:
Arrg!  He’s the Pirate Cupcake!  But not to fear, he’s a sweet pirate.  But move over vanilla and chocolate, there’s a new matey in the bakery case!

	Screen printed from an original design by me.  Unisex style Adult tee comes in S,M,L or XL.  100% cotton Gildan heavyweight tee.

name: Nervous Robot Screen Printed Plush
description:
He’s my original character of Nervous Robot.  Let him do the worrying for you.  He enjoys watching game shows and he idolizes R2-D2.

	Hand screen printed in black water based non toxic ink on soft felt.  Your choice of color, red, yellow, blue, green or hot pink.  Measures about 7” tall.  Comes with a hang tag explaining all about him.

name: Cheese Please Adult T Shirt
description:
Hand screen printed from an original design by me.  Show your polite love for cheese by wearing a Cheese, Please tee!

	Printed in black non toxic water based ink on a cheesey orangey tee.  Unisex style adult tee that comes in S, M, L or XL.  100% cotton Gildan heavyweight brand tee.

name: Gold Tooth Funny Bunny Easter Plush
description:
He’s the geekiest Easter Bunny you’ll every see.  But this version has a twist of a little bling-bling with his gold tooth and gold bow.
Hand screen printed from an original design by me. Printed in white ink on brown felt in non toxic water based ink.  Measures about 8” tall.  Comes wrapped like a real chocolate bunny but without the calories.  Just lots of toothy fun!
